name: Niranjan
specificRequirements:
Nanny Requirement for Infant (7 Months) – Bangalore
We are looking for a part-time nanny for our 7-month-old baby at our home in Bangalore.

Working Days: Monday to Friday
Timings: 10:00 AM to 6:00 PM

Responsibilities:
Provide attentive, loving care and supervision for the baby.

Engage the baby in age-appropriate, screen-free activities to support development (play, reading, singing, etc.).

Take the baby for short, safe walks within the premises or neighborhood.

Prepare and feed basic baby food (no major cooking required); handle bottle feeding of milk.

Handle diaper changes and ensure baby’s hygiene.

Soothe, comfort, and assist in putting the baby to sleep for naps.

Maintain cleanliness in the baby's area and manage baby laundry if needed.

Requirements:
Experience caring for infants (ideally with references); relevant certifications (such as child care, infant first aid) preferred.

Proficient in English, Hindi, or Tamil.

Must be non-smoker and maintain hygiene.

Should be engaging, patient, and attentive to baby’s needs.

Comfortable working in a home where parents may be working from home or in a hybrid schedule (there will always be a parent present).

Additional Information:
No major housework or cooking required, focus solely on child-related duties.
The role is for part-time, at-home care, not live-in.
Immediate start preferred; long-term commitment is appreciated.
